  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658600/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765025035\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658600/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765025035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658600/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765025035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2><br>Lanwmover game where player drive lawnmower and cut grass in big open world which contain grass, houses and other obstacles<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Drive lawnmover in open world and only job is to cut every cuttable grass in open world. After cutting all grass, it will respawn.<br><br>Lawnmover has also fuel consumption. Pick-up Jerry cans and add fuel. <br>After fuel is empty player will respawn to start location<br>There is score system that player can get score with any grass player has cutted. <br><br>Enjoy the game, cut all grass and be the lawnmower king......",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2><br>Lanwmover game where player drive lawnmower and cut grass in big open world which contain grass, houses and other obstacles<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Drive lawnmover in open world and only job is to cut every cuttable grass in open world. After cutting all grass, it will respawn.<br><br>Lawnmover has also fuel consumption. Pick-up Jerry cans and add fuel. <br>After fuel is empty player will respawn to start location<br>There is score system that player can get score with any grass player has cutted. <br><br>Enjoy the game, cut all grass and be the lawnmower king......",
